{"tid":914614,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"上唔到公屋,租緊個單位加租,點撚算?","createTime":"2018-11-24T12:25:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-25T05:12:48.000Z","uid":48234,"like":9,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d0afb37b3031c0e231b8a8ed261f0c85c2ec2772","tid":914614,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T12:25:35.000Z","msg":"喂,做麥難民囉,瞓街囉,仲諗?<br />\n公屋俾每日150蚑那蝗,唔知幾多隻不停影響社會治安嘅蝻搶鳩晒<br />\n你仲俾班業主個個月呃你4倍甚至更多租金?<br />\n繼續租樓,即係繼續推高個租金<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">一邊嘈租金貴,一邊繼續租<br />\n咁啲業主梗係唔撚怕你嘈啦,繼續加你租啦<br />\n用撚吓你個腦啦,租租</span></span>"},{"pid":"2760043bfb2d3c0c8a63d0d9b8591e02cef65855","tid":914614,"uid":164980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T12:28:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9a68feae69f70586da0e6cd313a903df4d979be6","tid":914614,"uid":48234,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2760043bfb2d3c0c8a63d0d9b8591e02cef65855","tid":914614,"uid":164980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T12:28:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T12:45:36.000Z","msg":"咩KOL?俾條link嚟睇睇"},{"pid":"bb6e1eb93ca1c2c807c43a86331b1183b6c44b77","tid":914614,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T12:49:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">唔駛諗實會有業主負鳩我評<br />\n梗係啦,我叫班租租用腦,你哋利益受損呀嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔撚好同我講你唔想睇到成M記都係麥難民,你係怕投資冇回報咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"00c7394df4a2437bb244f8012179050b369ae735","tid":914614,"uid":6420,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T13:23:28.000Z"